data.description: *CLICK 3D TOUR ABOVE* $3,000 Seller CLOSING CREDIT, 1% Interest Rate BUY DOWN & FREE APPRAISAL complements of preferred mortgage partner for 1st year of your mortgage. WATER FRONT, MODERN, 6 YRS YOUNG “Palisades Model” home cradled in GATED Verona community of Renaissance. Handsome MOVE IN ready home offers UPGRADES, almost 2100 sqft living space, 2 beds w/private en-suites, LARGE DEN, 2.5 baths, pavered driveway/walkway, HURRICANE IMPACT FRONT DOOR & HURRICANE SHUTTERS, contemporary TILE & LAMINATE FLOORING THROUGHOUT & WATER VIEWS from almost every room. Stunning curb appeal with LANDSCAPE CURBING & swaying palm trees will catch your eye, as you drive up to the home. LARGE GLASS FRONT DOOR welcomes you & your guests into this SPARKLING CLEAN & OPEN FLOOR PLAN home which boasts of 10’+ high ceilings. An open foyer flooded with FLORIDA SUNSHINE guides you naturally into the home, with WATER VIEWS readily seen. This home is METICULOUSLY MAINTAINED. TRIPLE SLIDING GLASS DOORS from the large living area & dinette create the perfect space to entertain or enjoy your own private retreat on the water. OVERSIZED Kitchen is OPEN, INVITING & ENGAGING as you are always right in the middle of everything! It boasts CONTEMPORARY SOLID WOOD cabinets for storage, granite countertops, an expansive ISLAND w/bar seating, stainless-steel appliances (includes NEW OVEN W/AN AIR FRYER OPTION)! CUSTOM LIGHTING, CEILING FANS & ARCHITECTURAL features are just a few of the upgrades. Gatherings for the holidays or dinners with friends are perfect for the intimate Dining room. OWNERS SUITE features a SERENE WATER VIEW, WINDOW TREATMENTS, DOUBLE WALK-IN CLOSETS w/CUSTOM SHELVING and a sitting area. The ensuite bathroom offers lots of personal space, w/SEPARATE VANITIES, PRIVATE water closet, spacious walk-in shower & large tub! SPLIT PLAN ENSUITE guest bedroom offers ultimate privacy for everyone, since it is on the other side of the home! Since this model offers a DEN & HALF BATH, it is one of the MOST POPULAR models.  A large laundry room w/granite countertops, utility sink & tons of storage space make handling the laundry task a breeze! But when it is time to enjoy the balmy sea breezes, nothing is better than your own SCREENED-IN PAVERED LANAI w/relaxing water views & sellers have decided that LANAI FURNITURE WILL CONVEY! Florida sunshine, grilling with friends & enjoying the wild life. It doesn't get much better than this! Living in Verona offers you a privately GATED community with its very own PRIVATE COMMUNITY POOL, but you are also part of the Renaissance community! "Club Renaissance" is a magnificent Mediterranean-style clubhouse. A full-service facility that includes a golf shop, swimming pool, spa, fitness center, exercise/dance/yoga room, indoor walking track & an outstanding restaurant. You also enjoy access to all Sun City Center amenities as well. Sun City Center is one of Florida's most popular active-living 55+ communities, with a range of recreational & fitness centers, 2 multi-million-dollar clubhouses & it even has a travel club. There are hundreds of "activity clubs", nearby shopping centers, golf courses, & endless entertainment resources all accessible by golf cart! It's the most perfect location being close to Tampa theaters, sporting events, dining, & award-winning beaches in Clearwater & Siesta Key, both recently voted the #1 beaches in the USA! CONVEYS with SALE OF HOME:  LANAI FURNITURE (NOT including TV and GRILLS)/Golf Cart Negotiable.
